dct_description_sm: Map 1: Map covers Old Man's Creek to General Cadwall Aders Island.Map shows grants, property names, and licenses. Birds Creek and Repaupo Creek are also pictured.

Map 2: Map covers area from the property of Widow Dix to the property of Isaac Kerns.Map depicts and names multiple properties and grants. A list of 38 people who have obtained licenses on Big Timber Creek at Westville is included on map.
